videos.description: Texas A&M guard Jalen Jones describes what it feels like to play in his final game at home and to clinch at least a share of the regular season SEC title with a 76-67 victory over Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Jones on SEC title: 'I'm just trying to hold back tears'
